          "customerName": "Haiyzee",
          "rating": 5,
          "title": "lanforge",
          "comment": "I’ve had an amazing experience getting my PC built by LANForge! From start to finish, Damian was super nice and extremely accommodating. He listened to what I had imagined my PC to look like and made it 10 times better. The entire process is so smooth, easy and stress-free. The PC itself is absolutely perfect! Everything was put together and packaged with so much care and attention to detail. The cable management is impeccable, and everything works perfectly right out of the box. It was delivered exactly when he said it would be, and I couldn’t be happier with how it turned out. I couldn't express my thanks and appreciate it more, thank you again! ",
          "isVerifiedPurchase": false,
